---
title: Che Buono Chicken Spaghetti with Grape Tomatoes & Italian Herbs
description: Our chefs have dreamed up the pasta equivalent of an Italian serenade, and it hits all the right notes. Al dente spaghetti is tossed with sautéed tomatoes and a garlicky, Italian herb-infused cream sauce. Of course, it wouldn’t be pasta night without plenty of Parmigiana; some gets stirred into the sauce, while the rest is sprinkled over top for a decadent garnish. Now that’s amore!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/608023b47b3b15615c41dfa4-a72e05e1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/che-buono-chicken-spaghetti-608023b47b3b15615c41dfa4-bb8a99b4.pdf
time required: 25 minutes
